name: 🚀 Feature Request
description: Suggest an idea or new feature for go-music-tui.
title: "[FEATURE]: "
labels: ["enhancement"]
body:
  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        Have an idea to make go-music-tui better? Please tell us about it!
        新しい機能のアイデアをお持ちですか？ぜひお聞かせください！

  - type: dropdown
    id: language
    attributes:
      label: 🌐 Preferred Language / 希望する対応言語
      description: Which language would you prefer to communicate in? (どちらの言語での対応を希望しますか？)
      options:
        - English (英語)
        - Japanese (日本語)
        - Either is fine (どちらでも可)
        - Other
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: problem
    attributes:
      label: 🤨 Is your feature request related to a problem? / 現状の困りごと
      description: A clear and concise description of what the problem is. (例:「〇〇の操作がしづらい」「〇〇が表示されなくて不便」など)
      placeholder: "e.g., I'm always frustrated when..."
    validations:
      required: false

  - type: textarea
    id: solution
    attributes:
      label: 💡 Proposed Solution / 提案する機能の内容
      description: A clear and concise description of what you want to happen. (どのような機能や画面表示が欲しいかを詳しく教えてください。)
      placeholder: Describe the solution you'd like to see...
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: alternatives
    attributes:
      label: 🔄 Alternative Solutions / 代替案（もしあれば）
      description: Any alternative solutions or features you've considered. (他に考えられる方法や、現状どうやって回避しているかなどがあれば教えてください。)
      placeholder: Describe any alternative solutions you've considered...
    validations:
      required: false

  - type: textarea
    id: context
    attributes:
      label: 📌 Additional Context / その他・参考資料
      description: Any other context, mockup screenshots, or examples from other TUI tools. (イメージ図のスクリーンショットや、他のツールの例などがあればここに貼ってください。)
      placeholder: Attach mockups or screenshots by dragging and dropping them here.
    validations:
      required: false
